### Step 2: Add or update code snippets

Create a new test file at `sdk/computelimit/Azure.ResourceManager.ComputeLimit/tests/Samples/Sample1_GettingStarted.cs`:

```csharp
// Copyright (c) Microsoft Corporation. All rights reserved.
