### Step 4: Validate

Run these commands in order:

1. `dotnet build sdk/computelimit/Azure.ResourceManager.ComputeLimit/`
2. `dotnet test sdk/computelimit/Azure.ResourceManager.ComputeLimit/ --filter TestCategory!=Live`
3. `eng/scripts/Update-Snippets.ps1 computelimit` — injects code from `#region Snippet:` tags into README placeholder blocks; check git diff after to confirm README updated
4. `eng/scripts/Export-API.ps1 computelimit` — regenerates public API listing files (no new public types expected here, but run to confirm)
5. `dotnet format sdk/computelimit/Azure.ResourceManager.ComputeLimit/` — ensures consistent formatting

